{"name":"Blade of Atropos","permission":{"default":0,"U5X07uKi3FMVWkQ1":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dcc-compendium.spell-tables.VoQExiURmacRa8lo"}},"img":"modules/dcc-core-book/assets/svg/game-icons-net/bouncing-sword.svg","description":"<h1>Blade of Atropos</h1><p><strong>Level:</strong> 1</p><p><strong>Range:</strong> Varies</p><p><strong>Duration:</strong> Varies</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 round</p><p><strong>Save:</strong> Will save vs. 15+CL</p><p><strong>Page:</strong> 351</p><br><p>The Blade of Atropos is gifted to those willing to do the work of the Fates, bringing an end to chaos-creatures and those bearing the mark of arcane corruption. Casting the spell requires a non-magical sword; if the blade is decorated with jewels and precious metals (worth no less than 1,000 gp), the caster receives a +2 bonus to his spell check. If the blade leaves the caster&rsquo;s hand, the spell immediately ends. Strength modifiers (positive or negative) have no effect on the caster&rsquo;s to hit roll or damage rolls while wielding the blade.</p><br><p><strong>Spell Data:</strong> @Compendium[dcc-core-book.dcc-core-spell-journals.Blade of Atropos]{Blade of Atropos}</p>","results":[{"_id":"iaGg7gE38swHMNRA","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Lost, failure, and patron taint.","collection":null,"weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false},{"_id":"FGtfazSUdfagwbvi","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Lost. Failure.","collection":null,"weight":10,"range":[2,11],"drawn":false},{"_id":"ZYhDzwkJ3JTJhaMj","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Attacks with the empowered blade are at a +1 to hit (+3 vs. chaos-creatures or corrupted casters) and inflict [[/roll 1d12]]+CL in damage. The spell lasts for [[/roll 1d3]]+CL rounds.","collection":null,"weight":2,"range":[12,13],"drawn":false},{"_id":"SVPC0iNi0fRtPwzj","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Attacks with the enchanted blade are at a +2 to hit (+4 vs. chaos-creatures or corrupted casters) and inflict [[/roll 1d14]]+CL in damage. The spell lasts