 enough to be ridden as a mount, provided the character has a saddle that overcomes the barbs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":4,"range":[24,27],"drawn":false},{"_id":"i2FoUnEVVgyuJw94","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Bobugbubilz sends a minor toadfiend (see stats on page 402). This horrid crossbreed of man and amphibian rises immediately from a muddy pit and lurches about chaotically, striking down foes in between croaking gurgles. It remains for one hour.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":2,"range":[28,29],"drawn":false},{"_id":"AKDUjtDCIQ331whe","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The evil god of amphibians sends an avatar (see stats on page 402). This dark-skinned monstrous toad covered in boils drops from above to attack the caster’s enemies. It remains for [[/roll 2d6]] rounds, during which time it fights ferociously.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":2,"range":[30,31],"drawn":false},{"_id":"wnX7urcC4qIOqmKf","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Bobugbubilz sends an avatar (see stats on page 402) and also imbues the caster with a supernatural burst of toad-strength. The caster gains a +6 bonus to Strength as long as the avatar remains present. The avatar, a dark-skinned monstrous toad covered in boils, drops from above to attack the caster’s enemies. It remains for [[/roll 2d6]] rounds, during which time it fights ferociously.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","resultId":"","weight":1,"range":[32,99],"drawn":false}],"formula":"1d20","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true}
